    <h3>Why Mentorship Matters</h3>
    <p>Mentorship is at the heart of our platform. It's a reciprocal relationship that empowers students to unlock their potential by connecting with experienced faculty members. Mentors offer guidance, share their knowledge, and provide valuable insights to help students thrive in their academic and professional lives.</p>
